               dh-python,
               python-all-dev,
               python-setuptools,
               python-cherrypy3,
               python-configobj,
               python-psutil,
               python-simplejson
Standards-Version: 3.9.6
Homepage: http://software.internet2.edu/bwctl
Vcs-Git: git://github.com/perfsonar/bwctl
