Package: bwctl2
Architecture: all
Depends: bwctl2-client, bwctl2-server, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Network measurement scheduler metapackage
 BWCTL is a command line client application and a scheduling and policy daemon
 that wraps various network measurement tools including iperf, iperf3, owamp
 ping and traceroute.

Package: bwctl2-shared
Architecture: all
Depends: python-cherrypy3, python-configobj, python-psutil, python-simplejson,
 python-pkg-resources, python-netifaces, python-radix, python-routes,
 iperf, iperf3, ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Description: bwctl shared components
 Shared components used by the bwctl server and client packages.

Package: bwctl2-client
Architecture: all
Depends: bwctl2-shared, ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Description: bwctl client
 bwctl command line tool for scheduling bandwidth measurements with a bwctl
 server.

Package: bwctl2-server
Architecture: all
Depends: bwctl2-shared, adduser, ntp, ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Recommends: iputils-ping, iputils-tracepath, traceroute
Suggests: owamp-server, owamp-client
Description: bwctl server
 bwctl server for scheduling bandwidth measurements.
